lock V8 engine]]'''&mdash;[[big-block]] (317/341/368), HD truck (279/302/317/332)\n* 1954&ndash;1964 '''[[Ford Y-block engine|Y-block V8]]'''&mdash;[[small-block]] Ford/Mercury/Edsel (239/256/272/292/312)\n* 1958&ndash;1968 '''[[Ford MEL engine|MEL V8]]'''&mdash;big-block Mercury/Edsel/Lincoln (383/410/430/462)\n* 1958&ndash;1976 '''[[Ford FE engine|FE V8]]'''&mdash;[[Mid block|medium-block]] Ford/Edsel\n** 1958&ndash;1971 Generation I (332/352/360/361/390)\n** 1962&ndash;1973 Generation II (406/410/427/428)\n** 1965&ndash;1968 [[Ford 427 side oiler]]\n** FT truck (330/359/361/389/391)\n** 427 SOHC**\n* 1958&ndash;1981 '''[[Ford Super Duty engine|Super Duty truck engine]]'''&mdash;big-block (401/477/534)\n* 1962&ndash;2000 '''[[Ford Windsor engine|Windsor]]'''&mdash;small-block (221/255/260/289/289HP/302/351W/[[Ford Boss 302 engine|Boss 302]]/427 aluminum)\n* 1968&ndash;1997 '''[[Ford 385 engine|385 V8]]'''&mdash;big-block (370/429/[[Boss 429]]/460/514)\n* 1970&ndash;1982 '''[[Ford 335 engine|335/Cleveland V8]]'''&mdash; small-block (351 Cleveland/400/351M/[[Ford Boss 351 engine|Boss 351]])\n** 1972&ndash;1985 '''[[Ford Australia]]''' produced Cleveland V8 engines 302/351 ([[Geelong]] plant)\n* 1983&ndash;2010 '''Ford/[[Navistar]] [[Diesel engine|Diesel]] V8'''\n** 1983&ndash;1987&mdash;6.9&nbsp;L [[International Harvester IDI|IDI (indirect injection)]]\n** 1988&ndash;1993&mdash;7.3&nbsp;L IDI\n** 1993&ndash;1994.5&mdash;7.3&nbsp;L IDI with Turbo\n** 1994.5&ndash;2003.5&mdash;7.3&nbsp;L DI (direct injection) \"[[Ford Power Stroke engine|Power Stroke]]\"\n** 2003.5&ndash;2009&mdash;6.0&nbsp;L DI \"Power Stroke\" (E and F-series vehicles)\n** 2008&ndash;2010&mdash;6.4&nbsp;L DI \"Power Stroke\" (F-series only)\n* 1991&ndash;present '''[[Ford Modular engine|Modular V8]]''' &mdash;[[Overhead camshaft|SOHC]]/DOHC 4.6/5.0/5.4/5.8&nbsp;L\n** 1997&ndash;present '''Triton V8'''&mdash;truck versions of the Modular\n** 2003-2004 '''[[Ford Modular engine#4.6.Terminator|Terminat